WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:03.200
Mom!

00:03.719 --> 00:04.785
Mom?

00:06.723 --> 00:09.076
Next Tuesday's fine.

00:09.726 --> 00:10.726
- Let's do that.
- Yeah.

00:10.760 --> 00:12.695
Keep him on the leash, honey.

00:12.729 --> 00:13.914
Thank you.

00:14.664 --> 00:16.082
Mom!

00:17.567 --> 00:18.867
Mom?

00:18.902 --> 00:20.769
Mom!

00:23.807 --> 00:25.307
It's okay, honey.

00:25.342 --> 00:27.876
It's okay. How can I help?

00:27.911 --> 00:30.157
I can't find my mom.

00:30.158 --> 00:32.159
- I don't know where she went.
- It's okay.

00:32.192 --> 00:33.794
We'll find her. What's your name?

00:33.828 --> 00:35.758
- Luna.
- Luna.

00:35.792 --> 00:37.197
That's a pretty name.

00:37.232 --> 00:40.000
What about your dad?
Do you know where he is?

00:40.399 --> 00:41.969
I don't have a dad.

00:42.003 --> 00:43.971
My dad died.

